commitResults.messageTitle: Fix bug in sorting empty strings
commitResults.messageBody:
Empty Strings are lexicographically less than
non-empty Strings. We modify the compareTo method
in EcName such that empty strings are more than
non-empty Strings. Users can see students with
non-empty values at the beginning of the list.
